# Alembic Migrations for DataAgent Studio

## Quick Start

```bash
# Generate a new migration (auto-detect schema changes)
cd backend
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add user preferences table"

# Apply all pending migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Rollback one migration
alembic downgrade -1

# Show current revision
alembic current

# Show migration history
alembic history --verbose
```

## SQLite vs PostgreSQL

- **SQLite**: Used for development; lightweight migrations also handled by `app.database.run_migrations()`
- **PostgreSQL**: Required for production with 200+ KBs; Alembic is the sole migration tool
